rComments: Roxanne really cares for her students, participating in her class is especially meaningful as she has a lot of experience in the field. It would be nice if she had a TA to help her with her technical difficulties (setting up the power points and video clips) or if she assigned two students each week.

Can be a little disorganized, and material may not always be covered, but she does an amazing job making sure the class is learning what everyone wants to learn. She demonstrates skills like no tomorrow, is in touch with how the class is feelings, and overall is an excellent prof!!
Best prof I have ever had
Wow...though you are hardly learning anything, she grades you harshly. I second the "don't be fooled" warning.
Seems friendly, but don't be fooled. Beneath all this politically correct, touchy-feely, mumbo-jumbo is a disgruntled, mediocre, and self-righteous teacher.

She is a very nice person, and fostered an excellent atomesphere in the classroom.  Very intelligent and a hard marker. Also extremely hard-working - possibly lives at the school.  Many people find her hard to read.
